<p><b>Paul Hindemith</b> (16 November 1895 – 28 December 1963) was a German <a href="/wiki/Composer" title="Composer">composer</a>, <a href="/wiki/Violist" title="Violist" class="mw-redirect">violist</a>, violinist, teacher, music theorist and <a href="/wiki/Conducting" title="Conducting">conductor</a>.</p>
